      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok that's still pretty vague. i'm looking at the logs and it's not just a timeout, it's like the connection is being reset by the peer. if you just add a 5-second timeout, aren't we just masking a deeper issue with how the multipart buffer is being handled? if i can't see the code changes, i'm not comfortable closing this ticket. can you just provide the actual code block for the new middleware logic so i can run it through our linter? we need this resolved and confirmed ASAP so i can move on to the deployment.",
      "source": "evaluator"
